% Test: Database Create, Use, Drop
% Category: 01_database
% Description: Tests basic database lifecycle operations

% Create and use a database
.kg create test_db
.kg use test_db

% Show current database
.kg

% List databases (should show default and test_db)
.kg list

% Insert some data to verify db is usable
+edge(1, 2).

% Query to verify
?- edge(X, Y).

% Switch away and drop
.kg use default
.kg drop test_db

% Verify it's gone
.kg list
